data.title: Georgia Government Transparency and Campaign Finance Commission
data.meta_description: Georgia Government Transparency and Campaign Finance Commission enforces the laws under its jurisdiction through discreet investigative proceedings and open hearings. The SEC's powers include assessment of civil penalties and administrative costs, ordering of remedial actions, suspension or revocation of lobbyist registration privileges, and where necessary, reporting of suspected violations of law to the appropriate law enforcement authority.
